MySQL Notes 

.RDBMS 
    .program that maintains a relational database 
    .uses SQL queries to access data in the database 
    >> it defines database relationships in form of tables 
        .tables related to each other based on data common to each other 

DB table - collection of related data entries consisting of columns and rows 
    .columns - holds specific info about every record in the table 
    .row/record - each individual entry that exists in a table 



